Count Number of Occurences:grep -c "Error" logfile.txt
Using Regular Expressions: egrep 'Error|Exception' logfile.txt
Case Insensitive Search: grep -i Error logfile
Searching patterns in zip file: zgrep -i Error *.gz
Search Whole word: grep -w ERROR logfile.txt
Display File Names which contains Pattern: grep -l ERROR *.log
Recursive search: grep -lra "Error" logfile.txt
